# Common Schema Use Cases [​](https://docs.moca.network/airkit/usage/credential/schema-use-cases#common-schema-use-cases)
Here are some popular schema types you might create:
### Membership Points Schema [​](https://docs.moca.network/airkit/usage/credential/schema-use-cases#membership-points-schema)
A comprehensive example showing how to create a schema for tracking membership points and tiers.
#### JSON-LD Context [​](https://docs.moca.network/airkit/usage/credential/schema-use-cases#json-ld-context)
json```
{
  "@context": [
    {
      "@version": 1.1,
      "@protected": true,
      "id": "@id",
      "type": "@type",
      "MembershipPointsCredential": {
        "@id": "https://your-domain.com/schemas/membership-points.json-ld#MembershipPointsCredential",
        "@context": {
          "@version": 1.1,
          "@protected": true,
          "id": "@id",
          "type": "@type",
          "vocab": "https://your-domain.com/vocab/membership-points#",
          "xsd": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#",
          "memberId": {
            "@id": "vocab:memberId",
            "@type": "xsd:string"
          },
          "totalPoints": {
            "@id": "vocab:totalPoints",
            "@type": "xsd:integer"
          },
          "tier": {
            "@id": "vocab:tier",
            "@type": "xsd:string"
          },
          "lastUpdated": {
            "@id": "vocab:lastUpdated",
            "@type": "xsd:dateTime"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

#### JSON Schema [​](https://docs.moca.network/airkit/usage/credential/schema-use-cases#json-schema)
